### Central Sierra Insurance – Commission API
### Use with the VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### ─── Health Check ──────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ─── Reference Data (GET lookup tables) ────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reference/

### ─── Single Commission Calculation ─────────────────────────────
### Replicates: XLOOKUP bonus rate (col F) + total with bonus (col G)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/commissions/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent_id": 101,
  "first_name": "Bob",
  "last_name": "Lingle",
  "branch": "Cameron Park",
  "sales_amount": 8000
}

### ─── Single Commission – Low Sales (below lowest tier) ─────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/commissions/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent_id": 999,
  "first_name": "Test",
  "last_name": "Agent",
  "branch": "Folsom",
  "sales_amount": 2000
}

### ─── Single Commission – High Sales (top tier) ─────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/commissions/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent_id": 125,
  "first_name": "Cheryl",
  "last_name": "Nevens",
  "branch": "Cameron Park",
  "sales_amount": 12000
}

### ─── Bulk Commission Summary ───────────────────────────────────
### Replicates: all agent rows + SUMIF branch totals + SUM/AVG/MODE/MEDIAN

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/commissions/summary
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agents": [
